name: .SNF File Extension
summary: Learn about .SNF files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Document created by Starry Night Pro, an astronomy application used to observe constellations; contains a viewing preference that alters the view of the sky, planets, and galaxies; includes gaze, zoom, viewing location, time and date, and time flow rate data.

content: To create an SNF file, select File → Save or Save As..., choose the save location, name the file, and click Save.
To open an SNF file, double-click it, or select File → Open..., navigate to the file, and click Open.
